OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers are likely this evening, which
OL,7,Fcould be heavy and thundery. Becoming
OL,8,Flargely dry overnight though. Some
OL,9,Flate sunshine between showers giving
OL,10,Fway to clear spells overnight. Patches
OL,11,Fof low cloud and fog developing in the
OL,12,Ffar west too.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FSome very warm to hot hazy
OL,15,Fsunshine. However, some misty low
OL,16,Fcloud is likely in the far west, and a
OL,17,Ffew heavy, perhaps thundery showers
OL,18,Fare possible during the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
