OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FWarm
OL,6,Fsunshine and just a small chance of a
OL,7,Fheavy, possibly thundery shower on
OL,8,FFriday. Turning cooler and more
OL,9,Funsettled this weekend. Showery and
OL,10,Fbreezy weather arriving from the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
